<h2>Ready to experience more this summer?</h2>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Whether you're hoping to enjoy some fresh mountain air in Austria, fill up on the best food in Italy, or soak up the scenery in Switzerland, an Inghams summer holiday allows you to see more and do more.</span></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Flights, transfers and accommodation included in our holidays </strong></span></p>
<h3 style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/9b99cf96ae554494aa4d403ba39b19ff" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9b99cf96ae554494aa4d403ba39b19ff}#Italy" title="Summer Sale 2022" data-anchor="#Italy">Italy</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/9b99cf96ae554494aa4d403ba39b19ff" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9b99cf96ae554494aa4d403ba39b19ff}#Austria" title="Summer Sale 2022" data-anchor="#Austria">Austria</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/9b99cf96ae554494aa4d403ba39b19ff" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9b99cf96ae554494aa4d403ba39b19ff}#Switzerland" title="Summer Sale 2022" data-anchor="#Switzerland">Switzerland</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/9b99cf96ae554494aa4d403ba39b19ff" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9b99cf96ae554494aa4d403ba39b19ff}#Slovenia" title="Summer Sale 2022" data-anchor="#Slovenia">Slovenia</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/9b99cf96ae554494aa4d403ba39b19ff" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9b99cf96ae554494aa4d403ba39b19ff}#France" title="Summer Sale 2022" data-anchor="#France">France</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13090971/summer-2022-lates-838x330.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/80bfe6923559475e8a6537a9720331bb" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Browse our best offers below and enjoy incredible value on your next holiday. You'll be <a data-udi="umb://document/fa72be9e45bc442089252c6a18a0d2ae" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fa72be9e45bc442089252c6a18a0d2ae}" title="In Safe Hands">In Safe Hands</a> when you book your Summer 2022 holiday with us, we've put extra measures in to offer flexibility and help keep you and your money safe. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></p>
<p><strong>Speak to a member of our UK based team on <span class="InfinityNumber">01483 791 111</span> or book online.</strong></p>
