<h2>Italy Summer Holidays</h2>
<h3>Unlock Italy's Magic</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13090982/italy-hero-838x280.jpg" alt="Italy 2022 holidays" data-udi="umb://media/38f9f6c1a2b542c3b57cc67344f7fe00" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This summer, get a healthy dose of la dolce vita. The crown jewel of the Mediterranean, Italy is a beautiful country rich in history, culture and art. <span>From city escapes to lake-side retreats, Inghams can help you experience the best of Italy. </span><a data-udi="umb://document/a832d2b81406467da84868b42472ba8f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a832d2b81406467da84868b42472ba8f}" title="Italy Holidays">View our top recommended resorts and hotels in Italy.</a></span></p>
<h3>Lake Garda</h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Lake Garda offers beautiful lake-side resorts and fantastic walking and cycling along its stunning shores.</span></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/2aca012aa9894e59bc41af54311c4240" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2aca012aa9894e59bc41af54311c4240}" title="Lake Garda"><strong>View Lake Garda Deals &gt;&gt;</strong></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></p>
<h3>Neopolitan Riviera</h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Discover the magical Neapolitan Riviera on a holiday to Italy, the perfect location to explore some of the most spectacular stretches of coastline in Italy and clifftop towns. </span></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/8734888d08974cd7b81babb75642ddbc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8734888d08974cd7b81babb75642ddbc}" title="Neapolitan Riviera"><strong>View Neopolitan Riviera deals &gt;&gt;</strong></a></p>
