<p><a name="Austria"></a></p>
<h2>Austria Summer Holidays</h2>
<h3><strong>Experience one of Europe's biggest gems</strong></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13090980/austria-hero-838x280.jpg" alt="Austria 2022 holidays" data-udi="umb://media/f998496ecfc5411996f0b3885e913601" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Walking and nature fans will appreciate Austria’s staggering mountainscapes and beautiful rural areas off the beaten track. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">This country may be small in size but it is big in beauty and culture. <a data-udi="umb://document/0f2a4fd0e16b4c1b8da4f3061a5b3fb4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0f2a4fd0e16b4c1b8da4f3061a5b3fb4}" title="Austria Holidays">View our top recommended resorts and hotels in Austria.</a></span></p>
<h3>Mayrhofen</h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Mayrhofen is an idyllic town, located in the Tyrol region of Austria. It is surrounded by a beautiful alpine backdrop, which makes it the perfect summer holiday destination.</span></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/ed6a7f99b73d494099a1efe3f5d4e6c4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ed6a7f99b73d494099a1efe3f5d4e6c4}" title="Mayrhofen Latest Deals"><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>View Mayrhofen deals &gt;&gt;</strong></span></a></p>
<h3>Kitzbühel</h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Kitzbühel is a great vacation destination for visitors to Austria. Located between Innsbruck and Salzburg, Kitzbühel makes a perfect base for sightseeing and exploring the wider area.</span></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/8c8b7abb379f45f09d279f2ab7c1dbeb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8c8b7abb379f45f09d279f2ab7c1dbeb}" title="Kitzbuhel Latest Deals"><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>View Kitzbühel deals &gt;&gt;</strong></span></a></p>
