<p><a name="Slovenia"></a></p>
<h2>Slovenia Summer Holidays </h2>
<h3>Experience the best of Slovenia</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13090983/slovenia-hero-838x280-lake.jpg" alt="Slovenia 2022 holidays" data-udi="umb://media/c1cd4d36b2ad4ed880cc9e76bfc6f20d" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Slovenia is the land of caves, lakes, castles and historic cities. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Its unique blend of folk culture and spectacular Alpine scenery will capture your heart and imagination. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Take part in local summer festivals and delight your taste buds with their tasty regional cuisine. <a data-udi="umb://document/971eed069c434e59a6268833efa31aee" href="/{localLink:umb://document/971eed069c434e59a6268833efa31aee}" title="Slovenia Holidays">View our top recommended resorts and hotels in Slovenia.</a></span></p>
