<p><a name="Switzerland"></a></p>
<h2>Switzerland Summer Holidays </h2>
<h3>Your Swiss adventure awaits </h3>
<p><img src="/media/13090984/switzerland-hero-838x280.jpg" alt="Switzerland 2022 holidays" data-udi="umb://media/26de1ff80ae442299010c1f3d4895297" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Make memories to last a lifetime in this alpine wonderland. Switzerland is famed for its snow-capped mountains, cuckoo clocks and chocolate delights. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">A country full of mixed cultures, food and traditions, you’ll find surprises around every corner. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Enchanting castles, world-class architecture and unforgettable scenic rail journeys - these are the moments you travel for. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><span>Explore. Relax. Unwind. There’s so much to see, do and discover in Switzerland. </span><a data-udi="umb://document/5c2bffaf42f5469c8bf10a42f3f6a589" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5c2bffaf42f5469c8bf10a42f3f6a589}" title="Switzerland Holidays">View our top recommended hotels and resorts in Switzerland.</a></span></p>
