<p><a name="France"></a></p>
<h2>France Holidays from </h2>
<h3>Discover the diverse beauty of France </h3>
<p><img src="/media/13090981/france-hero-838x330.jpg" alt="France 2022 holidays" data-udi="umb://media/0be798ad82c0481fb42ae408bd791366" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">With world renowned cuisine, gorgeous scenery to explore and plenty of outdoor activities, the French Alps are the ultimate summer destination. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Enjoy fresh mountain air and gaze upon flower-filled meadows and azure blue skies. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Whether you’re walking underneath the spectacular peaks of the Mont Blanc range in Chamonix, exploring Morzine by bike, or enjoying the tranquillity of Lake Annecy, you are sure to make unforgettable memories.</span></p>
<p>Let Inghams take you to the heart of the French Alps this summer. <a data-udi="umb://document/3094a12f5ae449a6bc8aff9a61dc2754" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3094a12f5ae449a6bc8aff9a61dc2754}" title="France Holidays">View our hand-picked hotels and resorts.</a></p>
